<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<!--
	  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
	  ║  CAPABILITIES iOS — Gestão YAHWEH (Bundle: com.gestaoyahwehios.app)║
	  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

	  1) Sign In with Apple (com.apple.developer.applesignin)
	     OBRIGATORIO pela Guideline 4.8 da App Store: apps que oferecem
	     Google Sign-In (ou outro social login) DEVEM oferecer Sign in
	     with Apple no iOS. Sem esta capability + provisioning profile
	     com a feature ativa, a revisao Apple rejeita.

	  ⚠️  PUSH NOTIFICATIONS — DESABILITADO TEMPORARIAMENTE (build 1516)
	  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
	  A capability `aps-environment = production` foi REMOVIDA deste
	  ficheiro porque o provisioning profile actual em uso na Codemagic
	  («GestaoYahwehBootstrap_1776438974») nao tem Push Notifications
	  habilitado, fazendo o `flutter build ipa` abortar com:
	    "Provisioning profile doesn't include the aps-environment
	     entitlement."

	  Consequencia: `firebase_messaging` NAO entrega pushes em iOS
	  enquanto isto estiver removido. Restantes funcionalidades (login,
	  Firestore, Storage) continuam a funcionar normalmente.

	  PARA REACTIVAR PUSH iOS:
	    1. developer.apple.com -> Identifiers -> com.gestaoyahwehios.app
	       -> marcar [x] Push Notifications -> Save.
	    2. Profiles -> regenerar .mobileprovision App Store (deve incluir
	       Push Notifications + Sign In with Apple).
	    3. Codemagic -> CM_PROVISIONING_PROFILE = Base64 do novo perfil
	       (ou ativar «Automatic code signing»).
	    4. Re-adicionar neste ficheiro:
	         <key>aps-environment</key>
	         <string>production</string>
	    5. Bump de build + novo deploy.

	  ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
	  ║  CHECKLIST APPLE DEVELOPER + CODEMAGIC                          ║
	  ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
	  ║  developer.apple.com → Identifiers → App ID                     ║
	  ║    com.gestaoyahwehios.app                                       ║
	  ║      [x] Sign In with Apple                                      ║
	  ║      [ ] Push Notifications  (a marcar quando regenerar profile) ║
	  ║                                                                  ║
	  ║  Profiles → criar/regenerar .mobileprovision (App Store) que     ║
	  ║  inclua Sign In with Apple (e Push Notifications quando voltar). ║
	  ║                                                                  ║
	  ║  Codemagic → variavel CM_PROVISIONING_PROFILE = Base64 do novo   ║
	  ║  perfil. (Ou ative «Automatic signing» na app config.)           ║
	  ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
	-->
	<key>com.apple.developer.applesignin</key>
	<array>
		<string>Default</string>
	</array>
</dict>
</plist>
